{"tid":1949706,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"身在醫院的菲傭 Jinkie Alhambra：跟從港府呼籲留家，卻因此被僱主傳染，出院無期，「真是諷刺」！","createTime":"2020-03-29T23:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T00:17:20.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"10bbe55139a96fa5131dd4843e9534381f8a4e23","tid":1949706,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T23:53:54.000Z","msg":"勞工處籲外傭放假留守僱主家中，減少社交接觸。不過對外傭而言，留家等於增加與僱主接觸，未必可減低感染機會。CNN訪問一位正在醫院治療、被僱主傳染的菲律賓家傭。家傭組織形容本港外傭正面對很多風險，卻欠缺保障。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200330/large/1585498262_9d09.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200330%2Flarge%2F1585498262_9d09.gif&h=d8f24f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCNN題為「港府指示家傭留家以免病毒擴散，但她們很多在家被僱主感染」的報道訪問了身在醫院的菲傭Jinkie Alhambra，48歲的她說，她跟從港府呼籲留家，卻因此被僱主傳染，「真是諷刺」。報道稱，至今香港已有13名菲傭確診，菲律賓駐港領事館表示，大部份都是被外遊回港的僱主傳染。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200330/ULMWWVTHSFVJS6YRKG33Z5BHNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200330%2FULMWWVTHSFVJS6YRKG33Z5BHNI%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=b4df9b58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200330%2FULMWWVTHSFVJS6YRKG33Z5BHNI%2F&h=71abb21a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200330/ULMWWVTHSFVJS6YRKG33Z5BHNI/</a>"},{"pid":"3e34050acd6eb0e037fab693e950e5e6dd4b770f","tid":1949706,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T23:54:22.000Z","msg":"Alhambra的僱主曾到印度，短暫回港後飛往加拿大，其後在加拿大確診。翻查資料，印度旅行團群組最少九人確診，Alhambra住在僱主位於碧瑤灣28座的寓所，確診後留醫瑪麗醫院。Alhambra希望盡快康復，她服食過醫治愛滋的抗病毒藥後本已好轉，但經兩次陰性測試結果後，第三次又發現體內存在病毒，出院無期。"},{"pid":"b3653845262edd50ea9cbcb0fb8fd03fca5a4619","tid":1949706,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T23:54:55.000Z","msg":"國際家務工聯會指，家傭正面對很多風險，要照顧長者及病人，但沒病假及失業保障，港府一萬元現金發放計劃也不能受惠。CNN又訪問另一位菲傭Acel Bungcayao，38歲的她在疫潮下失業，其僱主原是國泰機師，國泰停航後機師放無薪假，索性回澳洲家鄉，Bungcayao因此被炒。機師僱主容許她暫居其香港寓所，直至5月租約屆滿。"},{"pid":"11288b3973e70b24e02422d5e5b6c44e0c8f7a9e","tid":1949706,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T23:55:05.000Z","msg":"外勞事工中心社區關係主任唐曉昕也收到外傭求助，她們想放假外出而與僱主產生矛盾，僱主最後要求外傭辭職。亦有外傭反映已留家九星期，又說有留家會被要求進行清潔，經常得不到補水。"},{"pid":"7da76c47d7f690e2e5acba5192285d36bfe1b3b5","tid":1949706,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T23:59:14.000Z","msg":"印尼爆眼 個單印尼姐姐都無出黎幫拖啦<br />\n事不關己 當睇唔到"},{"pid":"ea8dc9d593e3f667d9607bb43ad92836bae529a1","tid":1949706,"uid":84006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T00:02:47.000Z","msg":"講到放假出街fing就唔會比僱主傳染到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4592dbd1ad4923c1fee5f303d04b380592803c07","tid":1949706,"uid":89869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea8dc9d593e3f667d9607bb43ad92836bae529a1","tid":1949706,"uid":84006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T00:02:47.000Z","msg":"講到放假出街fing就唔會比僱主傳染到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T00:06:29.000Z","msg":"會唔會係佢哋逢星期日集會做咗隱形帶菌者都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0fe596876abcb0f30ab5468a3eeedde078bef5","tid":1949706,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7da76c47d7f690e2e5acba5192285d36bfe1b3b5","tid":1949706,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T23:59:14.000Z","msg":"印尼爆眼 個單印尼姐姐都無出黎幫拖啦<br />\n事不關己 當睇唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T00:11:06.000Z","msg":"香港人<br />\n睇人仆街最開心<br />\n憎人富貴厭人貧<br />\n貪心不足蛇吞象<br />\n自己仆街怨人天<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6de0d7ab37c559fff56834c24733dba8f7122a","tid":19